Message: Hi, Iâ€™m the NewsBreak Ad Assistant. How can I help?

hello, for some reason my conversions stopped to be attributed in Newsbreak

Hi there! Let's try to figure out why your conversions aren't being attributed in NewsBreak. Could you please let me know which tracking platform or service you're using? This will help me provide more specific guidance.
I use postback with RedTrack setup
I wonder if you could see logs on your side

Thanks for letting me know you're using RedTrack. To troubleshoot your postback setup with NewsBreak, please ensure that your RedTrack configuration is correct. You can refer to the following guide for detailed steps on setting up a RedTrack postback with NewsBreak: [How to set up a RedTrack Postback on NewsBreak](https://help.newsbreak.com/hc/en-us/articles/24825901083277-How-to-set-up-a-RedTrack-Postback-on-NewsBreak). If everything seems correct and the issue persists, please double-check your tracking URL and parameters.

Unfortunately, I don't have access to logs on NewsBreak's side. However, I can help you troubleshoot your RedTrack postback setup. Please make sure that your postback URL is correctly configured and that the callback parameter is added to your ad's landing page URL. You can refer to the Event Tracking Debugging Steps article for more details: [Event Tracking Debugging Steps](https://help.newsbreak.com/hc/en-us/articles/25226963388813-How-to-integrate-a-general-NewsBreak-Postback). Let me know if you need further assistance!
can I talk to a human?

I'm here to help with whatever you need! Let me know your question, and I'll do my best to assist you right away. If you still need further assistance, you can email our support team at adsupport@newsbreak.com.
